`0Help for the Read Menu ------------------

<F> Read Forward    - Read messages in forward order starting with a
                      specified message number.
<R> Read Reverse    - Read messages in reverse order starting with a
                      specified message number.
<N> Read New        - Read new messages starting from the last message
                      you read.
<I> Read Individual - Read an individual message.  If you choose this
                      option, you will be prompted for which message
                      number to read.
<M> Read Marked     - Read messages that were marked by the system if
                      you didn't read messages addressed to you at login, or 
                      messages you marked manually using Scan/Mark option.
<S> Read Search     - Read messages in the fields:  To name, From name,
                      or Subject.  You will be prompted which field you want to
                      search on.
<T> Read Topics     - This lets you read messages organized by subject.
<X> Exit            - Exit to the previous menu.

Press ENTER to continue....`4
